OL,3,C'Catastrophic' levels of sewage
OL,4,Cdischarged in Welsh waters say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FAnalysis of Dwr Cymru's sewage
OL,8,Fdischarge figures shows the company
OL,9,Fdischarged sewage 118,276 times in
OL,10,F2024, an average of more than one
OL,11,Fsewage spill every five minutes.
OL,13,FThis equates to 968,340 hours.
OL,15,FNow an annual report by campaigners
OL,16,FSurfers Against Sewage (SAS) claims
OL,17,Fthat Dwr Cymru discharged sewage more
OL,18,Fthan any other water company in the UK
OL,19,Flast year
