OL,3,C'Catastrophic' levels of sewage
OL,4,Cdischarged in Welsh waters say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FThe water company has said that this
OL,8,Fis a result of a large number of rural
OL,9,Fcommunities in the country, which are
OL,10,Fserved by smaller sewerage networks
OL,11,Fand storm overflows.
OL,13,FThey also said that over the next five
OL,14,Fyears they will invest #2.5bn on
OL,15,Fprojects to improve the environment,
OL,16,Fincluding #889m on investigating and
OL,17,Fimproving storm overflows.
