OL,3,C'Catastrophic' levels of sewage
OL,4,Cdischarged in Welsh waters say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FThe majority of the UK uses a combined
OL,8,Fsewerage system where rainwater and
OL,9,Fwastewater from homes are transported
OL,10,Fin the same pipes. While this
OL,11,Ftypically goes to treatment plants,
OL,12,Fheavy rainfall can sometimes overwhelm
OL,13,Fthis system.
OL,15,FAs a result there are rules in which
OL,16,Fthe system is legally allowed to
OL,17,Foverflow occasionally, which sees the
OL,18,Fsewer discharge released into water
OL,19,Fsuch as rivers and the sea.
