OL,3,C'Catastrophic' levels of sewage
OL,4,Cdischarged in Welsh waters say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FHowever environmental campaigners and
OL,8,Fwild swimmers say the current level at
OL,9,Fwhich sewage water is being discharged
OL,10,Fis concerning and that Dwr Cymru have
OL,11,Fshowed a "lack of ambition" in
OL,12,Freducing current levels.
OL,14,FSAS said it received 1,853 sickness
OL,15,Freports through its Safer Seas &
OL,16,FRivers Service app last year ` an
OL,17,Faverage of five people a day.
