OL,7,FSome 331 people had to see a doctor
OL,8,Faccording to the report, with 79% of
OL,9,Fthem reporting that their doctor had
OL,10,Fattributed their illness to sewage
OL,11,Fpollution.
OL,13,FThe latest sewage figures from the
OL,14,Freport come as water bills rose by an
OL,15,Faverage of #86 this year for
OL,16,Fhouseholds, which regulator Ofwat has
OL,17,Fsaid is to help finance a a #104
OL,18,Fbillion upgrade for the sector.
