OL,4,Cdischarged in Welsh waters say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FGiles Bristow, CEO of Surfers Against
OL,8,FSewage, said: "The sheer lack of
OL,9,Fambition shown by Dwr Cymru Welsh
OL,10,FWater to reduce pollution shows they
OL,11,Fhave no shame over the catastrophic
OL,12,Flevels of sewage they are spewing into
OL,13,FWales' beautiful coastline, rivers and
OL,14,Flakes. With such clear mismanagement,
OL,15,Fit's no wonder that less than a
OL,16,Fquarter of people believe that their
OL,17,Fwater supplier has used their bill
OL,18,Fpayments responsibly.
