OL,3,C'Catastrophic' levels of sewage
OL,4,Cdischarged in Welsh waters say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,F"Welsh waters have been polluted for
OL,8,Ffar too long and the whole system is
OL,9,Fto blame. Dwr Cyrmu Welsh Water has
OL,10,Fbeen polluting regularly. A shambolic
OL,11,Fregulator has let them get away with
OL,12,Fit and the government is asleep at the
OL,13,Fwheel. It's time for change. With an
OL,14,Felection rapidly approaching,
OL,15,Fpoliticians in Wales need to stop
OL,16,Fstalling and start acting to get a
OL,17,Fgrip on this broken system."
