OL,4,Cdischarged in Welsh waters say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FNatural Resources Wales which
OL,8,Fregulates Dwr Cymru Welsh Water says
OL,9,Fit downgraded the water company since
OL,10,F2021 and has told them an improvement
OL,11,Fin performance is needed.
OL,13,FA spokesperson for Dwr cymru said:
OL,14,F"Both England and Wales are working to
OL,15,Ftackle issues surrounding storm
OL,16,Foverflows, with a slightly different
OL,17,Ffocus. Wales is focused on tackling
OL,18,Fstorm overflows that cause the most
OL,19,Fenvironmental harm first. In England,
OL,20,Fthe focus is on reducing the numbers
OL,21,Fof spills.
