OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,F"We operate over 2,300 storm overflows
OL,8,Fin Wales as we have a very high number
OL,9,Fof assets for a relatively small
OL,10,Fpopulation.
OL,12,F"Many of our rural communities are
OL,13,Fserved by smaller sewerage networks
OL,14,Fand storm overflows, which are
OL,15,Fessential to ensure networks do not
OL,16,Fbecome overwhelmed and flood
OL,17,Fproperties. A spill from a very small
OL,18,Frural overflow in Wales counts the
OL,19,Fsame as a huge storm overflow in a
OL,20,Flarge UK city that you could drive a
OL,21,Fbus though.
